依各家烤箱的不同,烘烤時間可做調整。"},{"pid":"d1d9485f7ce8e381b2b730313ab440bfdef72316","tid":138364,"uid":1408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:46:18.000Z","msg":"細女係咪又係屋企發脾氣呀"},{"pid":"b89d8fa1d3d649c19f94b228ddbccd3d09fce3dd","tid":138364,"uid":77820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/28/225044_5d9ac3e589cd323db8cfc67c23434a71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F28%2F225044_5d9ac3e589cd323db8cfc67c23434a71.jpg&h=d2ce0de7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n各位請善用起底功能<br />\n樓豬dse未考就生仔啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n此post已完"},{"pid":"9fd96756921b6e9625fc3de3077234eff3ea2d10","tid":138364,"uid":26161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:59:41.000Z","msg":"你講乜鳩"},{"pid":"07b02cd2fcbeffca2b23685ac61f8da0c47ec428","tid":138364,"uid":69985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:02:15.000Z","msg":"tum 返細女先啦，佢唔想彈琴啦"},{"pid":"292754124365babbfd5d667e528ce29fd3fc6206","tid":138364,"uid":1137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:02:19.000Z","msg":"搵米雪幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c78fcc93cf4cf82087b3b38322d012d02d360c","tid":138364,"uid":59165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:10:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/28/225044_5d9ac3e589cd323db8cfc67c23434a71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F28%2F225044_5d9ac3e589cd323db8cfc67c23434a71.jpg&h=d2ce0de7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n各位請善用起底功能<br />\n樓豬dse未考就生仔啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n此post已完</blockquote><br />\n18年後搵返樓豬 姐係佢未出世已經屌到人有左<img src=\"/assets/faces/n